      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TAW MAJOR (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with 12 wins and nine minors from 28 tries. In the money last time at this track (29.76) in a NG, finishing a 1.5 lengths third. Looks suited here and rates on top. RED ROCK RAZZLE (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (29.65) at this track behind CLASSIC ETHICS in a NG. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Must be included in calculations. WINSOME JET (3) was in the placings last time but three back produced a dominant 29.62 win over 520m at this track. Should be in this for a long way. ASCEND FERN (8) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
